---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Grade 304 Stainless Steel Wire Pegs"
  description="Grade 304 stainless steel wire pegs are suitable for outdoor use in most Australian conditions. Higher corrosion resistance than Grade 201 with twice the nickel content."
>

  <section class="py-24 px-6 bg-navy-50">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-teal-500 mb-4">Grade 304 · Medium</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-navy-900 leading-tight mb-6">Medium Grade Stainless Steel Wire Pegs</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-navy-600 leading-relaxed">The most popular choice for Australian households — tough enough to leave outside, in most conditions.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">

      <div class="bg-navy-50 rounded-2xl border border-navy-100 p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-6">Product specs</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4 border border-navy-100">
            <p class="text-navy-400 uppercase tracking-wider text-xs mb-1">Grade</p>
            <p class="font-semibold text-navy-900">304 Stainless Steel</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4 border border-navy-100">
            <p class="text-navy-400 uppercase tracking-wider text-xs mb-1">Wire Diameter</p>
            <p class="font-semibold text-navy-900">1.8mm</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4 border border-navy-100">
            <p class="text-navy-400 uppercase tracking-wider text-xs mb-1">Length</p>
            <p class="font-semibold text-navy-900">5.8cm</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4 border border-navy-100">
            <p class="text-navy-400 uppercase tracking-wider text-xs mb-1">Pack Sizes</p>
            <p class="font-semibold text-navy-900">24, 36 or 50 pegs</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-4">Is Grade 304 right for you?</h2>
        <p class="text-navy-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">Grade 304 is the middle ground — significantly more corrosion resistant than Grade 201, thanks to twice the nickel content. These pegs can be left outside on the clothesline in most Australian conditions.</p>
        <p class="text-navy-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">If you live more than 10km from the coast and want pegs you can simply leave on the line, Grade 304 is the right choice for you.</p>
        <p class="text-navy-600 leading-relaxed">If you live near the ocean or in a marine environment, step up to Grade 316.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-navy-50 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-8 border border-navy-100">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-4">Best for</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-navy-600 text-sm">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-500 font-bold">✓</span> Leaving pegs outside permanently</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-500 font-bold">✓</span> Most Australian outdoor conditions</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-500 font-bold">✓</span> Non-coastal areas</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-500 font-bold">✓</span> Households more than 10km from the ocean</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-red-500 font-bold">✗</span> Not suitable for coastal or marine environments</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-red-500 font-bold">✗</span> Not suitable for use on boats</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <a href="https://www.biome.com.au/collections/wire-pegs" target="_blank" class="bg-teal-500 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-teal-700 transition-colors text-lg">Buy Grade 304 Pegs at Biome →</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12 px-6 border-t border-navy-100 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto flex gap-4">
      <a href="/products/grade-201" class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal-500 hover:text-teal-700 underline underline-offset-4">← View Grade 201</a>
      <a href="/products/grade-316" class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal-500 hover:text-teal-700 underline underline-offset-4">View Grade 316 →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>